1,"korName":"글렌드로낙 오리지널 12년","comment":"첫 잔으로 가볍게 시작하는 위스키"},"x-field-style":"alcohol-card","x-display-name":"시음 위스키","properties":{"alcoholId":{"type":"integer","format":"int64","description":"알코올 ID","example":1,"x-field-style":"plain-number","x-display-name":"위스키 ID","x-graphql":true},"korName":{"type":"string","description":"알코올 한글명","example":"글렌드로낙 오리지널 12년","x-field-style":"plain-text","x-display-name":"이름","x-graphql":true},"engName":{"type":"string","description":"알코올 영문명","example":"GLENDRONACH ORIGINAL 12Y","x-field-style":"plain-text","x-display-name":"영문명","x-graphql":true},"imageUrl":{"type":"string","description":"알코올 대표 이미지 URL","example":"https://img.example.com/alcohols/1.png","x-field-style":"image-url","x-display-name":"이미지","x-graphql":true},"comment":{"type":"string","description":"시음 위스키 설명","example":"첫 잔으로 가볍게 시작하는 위스키","x-field-style":"long-text","x-display-name":"위스키 기대평"}},"required":["alcoholId","korName"]}}},"required":["eventDate","eventTime","barAddress","detailAddress","entryFee","capacity","applicationLink","guideText","alcohols"]}' AS JSON), 'alcohol', 1, 1);

